ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5398b4f48cad564729b204546c9624fbef826ea8","tid":2214727,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"林鄭：有司法獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}